This collection contains the entirety of Ragman's self-titled comics - v1 01-05, v2 01-08, v3 (Cry of the Dead) 01-06, and the Suit of Souls one-shot. There are also several selected appearances (most notably alongside Batman and his &quot;family&quot;), the entire run of the Shadowpact series (of which he is a team member), and three volumes of DCP Archive Editions compiled by Kritter. PLEASE NOTE - even though the DCP collections reprint material found in the torrent, I included them so that you can download either the issues themselves or the DCP archives as you see fit; you DO NOT need to download both. Quality-wise, they are roughly equal from what I saw as I glanced through, so it is entirely up to you. The full list of Ragman appearances are found in the link I provided above - I have added most of them except for the major events (like the Crisis stuff or Day of Judgement/Vengeance). Thanks to Kritter-DCP and many others for the original scans - please seed and enjoy! :-)

This fills a request by arrowgreen426.
